{"tid":840322,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"沈祖堯求學生「LEAVE NOW」","createTime":"2018-09-28T15:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T08:59:43.000Z","uid":49974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b46c7a104b4299c2bc1de85c8e39331067d47eb","tid":840322,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140929/large/29lp1p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140929%2Flarge%2F29lp1p5.jpg&h=0d8d4653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年輕人戴上眼罩、雨衣走上抗爭前線，並舉起雙手，無懼警方使用胡椒噴霧。何柏佳攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】八大校長會回應集會聲明時和理非非，只呼籲各方保持冷靜。中大校長沈祖堯昨日在個人facebook則留言，請學生立即離開。<br />\n<br />\n嶺大︰無法接受放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n中大校長沈祖堯昨日在晚上約7時許，即警方施放催淚彈段約一小時，在個人facebook留言&ldquo;my friends, my students, my children...in my tears I beg you...LEAVE NOW!&rdquo;（我的朋友、學生、孩子&hellip;我流淚求你們&hellip;立即離開）。沈祖堯昨晚透過大學公關發放公開信，指看見示威者和警方衝突有「說不出的難過」，也被學生的赤子之心感動，並呼籲學生撤離現場；並希望執法人員冷靜克制，以對話解決問題。<br />\n八大校長會昨日發聲明指，示威者和警方之間的衝突致有人受傷感傷心難過。原文指，「尤其是因示威者與警方之間的對立，而導致有人受傷和遭逮捕，我們感到傷心難過」。校長會指非常關注牽涉其中的學生及所有人士的安全和福祉，呼籲各方保持冷靜、進行溝通及避免行動升級，並以文明及和平的方式處理問題。<br />\n教院及科大設立熱線支援參與集會的學生，浸大指有老師在現場和學生保持聯絡。對於周一開始的罷課，嶺大指會維持正常運作，按實際情況作安排。嶺大協理副校長陳清橋，昨在集會期間吸入催淚氣體，表示對警方發放催淚彈的做法，無法接受。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140929/18883474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140929%2F18883474&d=LX%2BWfoYsR01hPJyzw8516ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=986e02a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140929%2F18883474&h=a2bad397\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140929/18883474</a>"},{"pid":"fbd677983c0f9e4ebee489287fe28b146fce5e87","tid":840322,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b072bfaa30e2f4887ffa7af7ac6f27fc9b34a9","tid":840322,"uid":49974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"要爆4，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb9ed324305d763920c79ac5b0e6c9d5922285e","tid":840322,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"讀咁多書 但去到咁高位既時候 大部份人都會無曬人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6e193460c8d9d0d0b8c075b990dab3e532d208","tid":840322,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec892216c1a5a7d3b2f18c04cb62ceb1e31649a","tid":840322,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T02:33:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7993b0c1273eb9f3efdaf935e63bd89a451558","tid":840322,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"回名帶未"},{"pid":"86c867a66bf5a2209a688007bde24dde3986bf55","tid":840322,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7993b0c1273eb9f3efdaf935e63bd89a451558","tid":840322,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"回名帶未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"回夠帶未"}]}